casebody.data:
MANASQUAN SAVINGS BANK, Plaintiff,
v.
Lynn SMITH, et al., Defendants-Movants. M-801/802 September Term 2017
079551 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 12, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying indigent status (M-801) is denied. Defendant must submit the filing fee of $250 on or before March 19, 2018; and it is further

ORDERED that the miscellaneous motion to file an amendment to the petition for certification (M-802) is denied.
